玩開生存Game既你, 入黎Discord一齊玩<br />\n幫手做大個高登仔基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"abe47e73c2cea7bbe8b46fd9ee2135f65c006536","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66ce52cde6482654d03bce75f66f4033827f589","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab1f4737e41e34dfd7095a2fa22ce82d95d8755","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4905f170bee0277e43db4dc62bb3d338c726a8","tid":101660,"uid":22548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:24:58.000Z","msg":"好似幾正！留名"},{"pid":"b7df5d83f1cf11ba5f87a99d2eb485dbacbf3dfd","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似幾正！留名</blockquote><br />\n買黎一齊玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997e066bd8149aee6bdb28f22a3126dc28839c2e","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db988a724f3f664c5069ae50aeec69f4c47bc39","tid":101660,"uid":70687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"有無折?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNTzu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNTzu.gif&h=9d0c22ef&s={SIZE}\" /> ???"},{"pid":"3e4273a5883284602b88389ad50f30b49c8e75ef","tid":101660,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無折?<img src=\"